lexitreks.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Magnifique-III-twin-2-300x200.jpg" alt="Magnifique III - twin" width="300" height="200"></a></p><p>Magnifique III – twin</p><p>The lower deck features 14 twin bedded cabins (approx. 11m²) and 2 single cabins. All are well-appointed and equipped with en-suite facilities, individually regulated air conditioning, flat screen TV, mini-safe and hairdryer. They each have one or two portholes which will be locked for safety reasons. Some of these cabins are able to accommodate a third bunk bed.</p><p>5 larger, upper deck suites are also available. They feature twin beds and occupy approximately 14m² and include larger windows, which can be partially opened, a small sitting area, en-suite shower/wc, individually regulated air conditioning, flat screen TV, mini-safe and hairdryer.</p><p><a href="https://flexitreks.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Magnifique-III-upper-deck-suite-3.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="https://flexitreks.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Magnifique-III-upper-deck-suite-3-300x200.jpg" alt="Magnifique III - upper deck suite" width="300" height="200"></a></p><p>Magnifique III – upper deck suite</p><p>Certain cabins can also be booked as a double (twin beds pushed together). Please request this at the time of booking</p><p>On the upper deck, there is a tastefully decorated salon with restaurant, bar and a lounge with wide screen TV, large windows to enjoy the scenery and free Wi-Fi. Large doors open onto a partially roofed sundeck.</p><p>On the top deck, you will find a whirlpool/Jacuzzi and deckchairs to relax.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Meals:</strong></p><p>On all three vessels, a hearty breakfast is provided each morning along with a packed lunch to take with you on the daily rides. A three-course meal is served each evening apart from one when you are free to step ashore and make your own arrangements – the crew will happily recommend restaurants on this evening.</p><p>Daily complimentary coffee and tea.</p><p><strong>On-board payments:</strong> Cash and debit/credit cards accepted.</p>
