553	151	accommodation	<p>This tour operates on the <em>Zwaantje, </em>a comfort class barge. More images of the barge can be found the gallery.</p>\n<p><strong>Zwaantje (comfort)</strong></p>\n<p>The <em>MS Zwaantje</em> is a comfortable boat offering a good standard of accommodation and facilities. She has 12 air-conditioned cabins on the lower deck; 10 are twin cabins with two single beds, 2 are doubles. All cabins have individual air conditioning, en-suite shower, toilet and wash basin.  The twin cabins have fixed windows while the two doubles have windows that can be opened. A few of the twin cabins are available for single use.</p>\n<p>On the main deck a warm and cosy atmosphere pervades throughout. There’s a comfortable, air-conditioned salon with large, panoramic windows, a restaurant area, lounge area and small bar. Free Wi-Fi is available in the salon although the quality of the connection does vary depending on the location of the barge.</p>\n<p>On the spacious sun-deck there are tables and chairs for relaxing in the fresh air, you can also step into the wheelhouse to watch Martijn, the skipper, at work.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Meals\n</strong>A hearty breakfast is provided each morning, along with a packed lunch to take with you on the daily rides. A three-course meal is served each evening in the dining area.</p>\n<p>Daily complimentary coffee and tea is available until 4pm.</p>
